javascriptcalculator
====================

Author: Nicholas Meyer

A reverse polish notation calculator written in javascript.
Uses responsive css to adapt the app size to any device.

Features:
---------
 * Should display well on any device (assuming reasonably current browsers)
 * Touch optimized on most mobile devices
 * Keyboard input on supported browsers

Known issues:
-------------
 * Decimal display can be problematic on mobile-sized browsers
 * Error messages don't always display cleanly when users cause another error
   message before the first is dismissed
